PurchasingStandardCostCalculation is a BusinessTask
    owned by po

    Patterns
        implements ManualTransaction
        implements StaticJava
            is report for InventoryManager, PurchasingManager, Receiver, Buyer, SupplyManagementProcessor, ApplicationAdministrator, SupplyManagementViewer, Purchasing
                category is "Period_\Close"
                report name is "StandardCostCalculation"
				Description
                    Calculate and create a reversing journal entry for the difference between the standard cost and the purchase order cost.
                    This calculation is for purchase order lines that have a Matched Not Received (MNR) or Received Not Invoiced (RNI) quantity that is greater than zero.
            Reports
                PurchasingStandardCostCalculationReport
                GlobalLedgerSummaryPostingReport

    Parameters
        Company                 is a PurchasingCompany 
        UpdateOption            is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                UpdateMode value is "Y"
                ReportMode value is "N"
        RunOption               is AlphaRight size 1
            States
                MnrOnly   value is "1"
                    default label is "MNR Only"
                RniOnly   value is "2"
                    default label is "RNI Only"
                MnrAndRni value is "3"
                    default label is "MNR and RNI"
        MnrProcLevel            is a PO139MnrProcLevelArray
        RniProcLevel            is a PO139RniProcLevelArray

    Parameter Rules
        Company
            required
        UpdateOption
        	initial value is "N"
            default to "N"
        RunOption
        	initial value is "1"
            default to "1"

    Actions
        PurchasingStandardCostCalculation is a Set Action
            allow unlimited concurrency
